HEADWORD: Pantler
<hw>Pan"tler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>panetier</ets>. See <er>Panter</er>, <er>Pantry</er>.]</ety>
<def>The servant or officer, in a great family, who has charge of the
bread and the pantry.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
